flowchart TD
    subgraph H[API Harness]
        R[Receive Request] --> I[Interact with Kernel]
        I -->|Get Intent/Assumptions| Proc[Process Request]
        Proc -->|Need Data| S[Storage Harness]
        S -->|Returns Data| Proc
        Proc -->|Log Decision| K[Knowledge Harness]
        K -->|Ack| Proc
        Proc --> SResp[Send Response]
    end
    subgraph KH[Kernel Hooks]
        I
    end
    style H fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#1565c0
    style KH:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px